settings.title: What is your return policy?
settings.answer:
Returns are accepted for most items, except for Replacement Cushions, Umbrellas, Patio Furniture, Pre-Cut Straps and Replacement Slings (because they are custom made to your dimensions).

Read about which items are returnable, and how to return them here:
https://www.sunnilandpatio.com/pages/shipping-terms

settings.title: What are your shipping details?
settings.answer:
All shipping fees are based on the contiguous United States standard shipping rates by package weight.

Free Shipping Applied on:

Furniture orders over $500

Non-Furniture orders over $150

All Replacement Cushion orders

Normal delivery time once shipped 3-10 days via USPS, UPS, or FedEx.

settings.title: Do you ship to Canada?
settings.answer: Unfortunately, we only ship to the Continental US
